            "title": "港鐵188億港元公募債券定價2.88%至4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港鐵(00066)今天(22日)宣布，昨天成功為逾188億港元企業綠色債券定價，是港鐵首次發行公募港元債券。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260315_CR_source_web_MTR5.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260315_CR_source_web_MTR5.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">債券分5 年、10年及30年，港鐵表示，債券獲標準普爾及穆迪分別評為「AA+」及「Aa3」級。其中，逾83億港元5年期債券、75億港元10年期債券及30億港元30年期債券，票息分別為2.88%、3.3%及4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今次是港鐵首次發行公募港元債券，亦是港元債券市場歷來最大單一交易規模發行；各年期債券的發行規模，亦打破了同年期債券在港元市場發行規模的紀錄。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港鐵表示，發行所得款項將按港鐵《可持續融資框架》，用作支持合資格的綠色投資項目。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15904346-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5188%e5%84%84%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e5%85%ac%e5%8b%9f%e5%82%b5%e5%88%b8%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b92-88%e8%87%b34",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/bplib_20250313-173936_202502_MTR__5_source-bp_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 11:50:09",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股跌轉升  深股重上萬五關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股低開後轉升，深股重上15000關，兩市成交合計15823.32億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日升10點或0.24%，報4095，今早以4074點開市，跌10點或0.25%，早段見4074，跌11點或0.26%，為半日低位，隨即反覆向上，最高見4096，升11點或0.26%，為上午高位，半日成交6766.75億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日報15076，升94點或0.63%，今早開市報14897點，亦跌84點或0.56%，已為上午低位，隨即彈升至15061，升79點或0.52%，為上午高位，半日成交9056.57億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升14點或0.3%，報4782，今早開跌16點或0.35%，開報4751點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日升23點或0.63%，報3712點，今早開市報3660點，跌28點或0.77%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15904321-a%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 11:35:17",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "GUM：4月份強積金暫時人均約賺2.07萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">強積金顧問GUM發表最新報告，指出截至本月17日，GUM強積金綜合指數於4月份暫升6.5%，估計強積金成員4月份暫時人均約賺2.07萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15904305-gum%ef%bc%9a4%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e5%bc%b7%e7%a9%8d%e9%87%91%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e4%ba%ba%e5%9d%87%e7%b4%84%e8%b3%ba2-07%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
